name: Personalised Baby Bag or Pram Charm Pin with Gift Box
description:
Handmade Personalised Baby Bag or Pram Charm


comes with a flat pack pillar box and charm comes wrapped in tissue paper.

Choose your name, upto about 10 letters, i do have styles for sale for longer names.

This charm is made on a 50mm silver coloured Nappy Pin

With 4 tibetan silver baby themed charms including a teddy, dummy, baby feet & pram

These are decorated with either pink or blue beads which are separated by a clear bead - there is an "other" option, please choose this is you require any other colour other than pink or blue then please let me know.
